Package: MixLS
Title: Mixed-Effects Location Scale Models
Version: 1.1.0
Authors@R: 
    person("Jianan", "Rui", , "jiananrui@uchicago.edu", role = c("aut", "cre"))
Description: Fits mixed-effects location scale models using a three-stage
    estimation procedure, allowing for both within-subject and
    between-subject variance heterogeneity. Methodologies are based on the
    work of Hedeker and Nordgren (2013) <doi:10.18637/jss.v052.i12>.
